/*==============================================================*/

(

);

/*==============================================================*/

(
employee_id
);

alter table manager add constraint "FK_MANAGER_经理-员工_EMPLOYEE" foreign key (employee_id)
references employee (employee_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
